5. Why is clean data important for dashboards and machine learning?

Dashboards:

Dirty data → Charts show NaN → Users confused ❌
Clean data → Smooth visuals → Professional app ✅

Machine Learning:

Missing values → Model crashes
Duplicates → Biased predictions  
Wrong types → Training fails

Streamlit Reality:

Users upload ANY CSV → Your app must handle mess → Clean first!

Golden Rule: Clean → Analyze → Visualize (always this order!)

Clean data = Trustworthy dashboard + happy users! ✨📊

